('1 Samuel', 22, 'kids', 1, 'After leaving Gath, David hid in a cave. What was the name of that cave?', 'Adullam', 'Engedi', 'Makkedah', 'Rimmon', 'a', '1 Samuel 22:1 — "David therefore departed thence, and escaped to the cave Adullam."'),
('1 Samuel', 22, 'kids', 2, 'About how many men came to join David at the cave?', 'About four hundred men', 'About one hundred men', 'About one thousand men', 'About fifty men', 'a', '1 Samuel 22:2 — "And every one that was in distress, and every one that was in debt, and every one that was discontented, gathered themselves unto him; and he became a captain over them: and there were with him about four hundred men."'),
