('1 Samuel', 28, 'kids', 3, 'What sad news did the spirit of Samuel tell Saul about the coming battle?', 'That Israel would be defeated and Saul and his sons would die the next day', 'That Saul would be captured but later released by the Philistines', 'That only Jonathan would die and Saul would escape to the hills', 'That the battle would end in a draw and Saul would have one more year to reign', 'a', '1 Samuel 28:19 — "Moreover the LORD will also deliver Israel with thee into the hand of the Philistines: and to morrow shalt thou and thy sons be with me: the LORD also shall deliver the host of Israel into the hand of the Philistines."');
